The putrid waters of the cataclysm began to take shape, a sprawling urban entity emerged from the mire.
The sewage and waste accumulated over centuries began to take shape, form coalescing into towering structures, spires, and grand architecture.
And thus, Reio Degen Ero was born – a city constructed from the very essence of human waste.
